org.hkijena.jipipe.api.data

Class JIPipeDataSlot

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.data.JIPipeDataSlot

  • public class JIPipeDataSlot
extends Object
    A data slot holds an JIPipeData instance. Slots are part of an JIPipeGraphNode
